{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01AYfdo2C17a8MVpqhMBneMB","type":"tool_result","content":"     1→# Gap Analysis: 001-coinflip — Coinflip\n     2→\n     3→- **Date**: 2026-02-26\n     4→- **Spec status**: Done\n     5→- **Previous analysis**: 2026-02-18 (pre-004 rewrite)\n     6→\n     7→## Implementation Inventory\n     8→\n     9→### On-Chain Instructions\n    10→\n    11→| Instruction | Program | File | Line |\n    12→|------------|---------|------|------|\n    13→| initialize_config | coinflip | programs/coinflip/src/instructions/initialize_config.rs | 24 |\n    14→| create_match | coinflip | programs/coinflip/src/instructions/create_match.rs | 28 |\n    15→| join_match | coinflip | programs/coinflip/src/instructions/join_match.rs | 25 |\n    16→| claim_payout | coinflip | programs/coinflip/src/instructions/claim_payout.rs | 55 |\n    17→| cancel_match | coinflip | programs/coinflip/src/instructions/cancel_match.rs | 24 |\n    18→| timeout_cancel | coinflip | programs/coinflip/src/instructions/timeout_cancel.rs | 32 |\n    19→| force_close | coinflip | programs/coinflip/src/instructions/force_close.rs | — |\n    20→| initialize_platform | platform | programs/platform/src/instructions/initialize_platform.rs | 25 |\n    21→| create_player_profile | platform | programs/platform/src/instructions/create_player_profile.rs | 24 |\n    22→| update_player_profile | platform | programs/platform/src/instructions/update_player_profile.rs | 20 |\n    23→\n    24→**Architecture**: 3-tx flow — create → join(+Orao VRF request) → claim(+VRF read + settle). The previous `resolve_match` instruction was deleted in the 004 shared-infrastructure rewrite; resolution is now handled at claim time by reading Orao VRF randomness on-chain.\n    25→\n    26→### Shared Crate\n    27→\n    28→| Export | Module | File | Line |\n    29→|--------|--------|------|------|\n    30→| SIDE_HEADS / SIDE_TAILS | constants | shared/src/constants.rs | 2-3 |\n    31→| PHASE_WAITING / LOCKED / SETTLED / CANCELLED | constants | shared/src/constants.rs | 6-9 |\n    32→| LOCK_TIMEOUT_SECONDS (120) | constants | shared/src/constants.rs | 12 |\n    33→| from_randomness | constants | shared/src/constants.rs | 15 |\n    34→| TOTAL_FEE_BPS (300) | fees | shared/src/fees.rs | 5 |\n    35→| calculate_fee | fees | shared/src/fees.rs | 12 |\n    36→| split_fee | fees | shared/src/fees.rs | 17 |\n    37→| TIER_AMOUNTS [6 tiers] | tiers | shared/src/tiers.rs | 5 |\n    38→| get_tier_amount | tiers | shared/src/tiers.rs | 17 |\n    39→| lifecycle::transition | lifecycle | shared/src/lifecycle.rs | — |\n    40→| escrow (transfer helpers) | escrow | shared/src/escrow.rs | — |\n    41→| timeout::is_expired | timeout | shared/src/timeout.rs | 12 |\n    42→| pause::check_not_paused | pause | shared/src/pause.rs | 13 |\n    43→| vrf_orao (read_orao_randomness, is_fulfilled) | vrf_orao | shared/src/vrf_orao.rs | 20 |\n    44→| commit_reveal | commit_reveal | shared/src/commit_reveal.rs | — |\n    45→| cpi (update_player_profile CPI) | cpi | shared/src/cpi.rs | — |\n    46→\n    47→### Game Engine Exports\n    48→\n    49→| Export | Package | File | Line |\n    50→|--------|---------|------|------|\n    51→| COINFLIP_PROGRAM_ID | game-engine | packages/game-engine/src/coinflip.ts | 10 |\n    52→| getMatchPda | game-engine | packages/game-engine/src/coinflip.ts | 25 |\n    53→| getConfigPda | game-engine | packages/game-engine/src/coinflip.ts | 36 |\n    54→| getEntryAmount | game-engine | packages/game-engine/src/coinflip.ts | 48 |\n    55→| calculatePotentialPayout | game-engine | packages/game-engine/src/coinflip.ts | 55 |\n    56→| getOppositeSide | game-engine | packages/game-engine/src/coinflip.ts | 65 |\n    57→| determineWinnerFromRandomness | game-engine | packages/game-engine/src/coinflip.ts | 72 |\n    58→| CoinflipIDL / PlatformIDL | anchor-client | packages/anchor-client/src/index.ts | 10 |\n    59→| Coinflip / Platform types | anchor-client | packages/anchor-client/src/index.ts | 6-7 |\n    60→\n    61→### Frontend Components\n    62→\n    63→| Component | File | Line |\n    64→|-----------|------|------|\n    65→| CoinflipProvider / useCoinflip | features/coinflip/context/CoinflipContext.tsx | 69, 362 |\n    66→| CoinSideSelector | features/coinflip/components/CoinSideSelector.tsx | 19 |\n    67→| CoinAnimation | features/coinflip/components/CoinAnimation.tsx | 20 |\n    68→| OpenMatchesList | features/coinflip/components/OpenMatchesList.tsx | 31 |\n    69→| MatchCard | features/coinflip/components/MatchCard.tsx | 13 |\n    70→| ActiveMatchView | features/coinflip/components/ActiveMatchView.tsx | 12 |\n    71→| chain.ts (instruction builders + queries + claimable matches) | features/coinflip/utils/chain.ts | 187-310 |\n    72→| verification.ts (verifyMatch + VerificationResult) | features/coinflip/utils/verification.ts | — |\n    73→| helpers.ts (truncateAddress, getOppositeSide) | features/coinflip/utils/helpers.ts | 3, 7 |\n    74→| CoinflipPage | pages/CoinflipPage.tsx | 450 |\n    75→| FairnessPage (coinflip VRF verification section) | App.tsx | — |\n    76→\n    77→### Tests\n    78→\n    79→| Test | Type | File | Status |\n    80→|------|------|------|--------|\n    81→| initialize_config (1 test) | bankrun | solana/tests/coinflip.ts:360 | passing |\n    82→| create_match (4 tests) | bankrun | solana/tests/coinflip.ts:379-435 | passing |\n    83→| join_match (3 tests) | bankrun | solana/tests/coinflip.ts:461-513 | passing |\n    84→| claim_payout (9 tests, incl. CPI) | bankrun | solana/tests/coinflip.ts:554-757 | passing |\n    85→| cancel_match (3 tests) | bankrun | solana/tests/coinflip.ts:793-827 | passing |\n    86→| timeout_cancel (3 tests) | bankrun | solana/tests/coinflip.ts:855-909 | passing |\n    87→| full lifecycle (3 tests) | bankrun | solana/tests/coinflip.ts:934-985 | passing |\n    88→| platform program (5 tests) | bankrun | solana/tests/platform.ts:97-203 | passing |\n    89→