lance | SATISFIED | CoinflipContext.tsx:206 joinMatch, chain.ts:241 buildJoinMatchTx |\n   115→\n   116→### FR-3: Flip Resolution\n   117→\n   118→| # | Criterion | Status | Evidence |\n   119→|---|-----------|--------|----------|\n   120→| 1 | Flip begins immediately when both players committed | SATISFIED | join_match embeds Orao VRF request CPI; frontend polls until randomness fulfilled. 3-tx flow: create→join(+VRF)→claim(+settle). |\n   121→| 2 | VRF determines the outcome | SATISFIED | Orao VRF integrated via shared vrf_orao module. claim_payout reads Orao randomness account + derives winner via from_randomness. |\n   122→| 3 | Result is deterministic and reproducible from VRF seed | SATISFIED | from_randomness(byte) is pure deterministic (shared/src/constants.rs:15). Orao randomness account persists on-chain. verification.ts re-derives result and confirms VRF fulfillment. |\n   123→| 4 | Flip animation plays with coin rotation and landing | SATISFIED | CoinAnimation.tsx:20 CSS 3D transform with spinning-heads/spinning-tails classes, dual faces |\n   124→\n   125→### FR-4: Settlement and Payout\n   126→\n   127→| # | Criterion | Status | Evidence |\n   128→|---|-----------|--------|----------|\n   129→| 1 | Winner payout = total_pool × 0.97 (3% fee) | SATISFIED | claim_payout.rs:55, fees.rs:5 TOTAL_FEE_BPS=300, test coinflip.ts:554 |\n   130→| 2 | Platform fee collected to treasury PDA | SATISFIED | claim_payout.rs treasury transfer, coinflip.ts:554 |\n   131→| 3 | Payout eligibility recorded on-chain | SATISFIED | state.rs winner+claimed fields, claim_payout CPI to update_player_profile |\n   132→| 4 | Winner can claim funds successfully | SATISFIED | claim_payout.rs:55, CoinflipContext.tsx:268, coinflip.ts:554 |\n   133→| 5 | Either player can trigger settlement (loser not blocked) | SATISFIED | claim_payout.rs caller validated as creator OR opponent, payout always goes to winner |\n   134→| 6 | Settlement is idempotent (no double-settle) | SATISFIED | error.