ports paste-a-tx-signature verification. | 2026-02-26 |\n   200→| Quick rematch (FR-7.6) | \"Play Again\" button in ActiveMatchView. Creates new open match with same tier/side via existing createMatch action. | 2026-02-26 |\n   201→| Timeout safety net | timeout_cancel instruction: either player can cancel LOCKED match after 2 min timeout if VRF unfulfilled. Refunds both players. Uses shared::timeout::is_expired + shared::vrf_orao::is_fulfilled guards. | 2026-02-19 |\n   202→| Claimable matches | fetchClaimableMatches() in chain.ts with dual memcmp queries (creator/opponent). \"Your Matches\" section in CoinflipPage with claim/cancel/view actions. | 2026-02-26 |\n   203→\n   204→## Deferred Items\n   205→\n   206→| Item | Deferred To | Target Spec | Target Status | Stale? |\n   207→|------|-------------|-------------|---------------|--------|\n   208→| Estimated wait time (FR-6.5) | post-MVP polish | none specified | — | UNTRACKED |\n   209→| Spinning sound (FR-8.1) | later spec | dedicated audio spec | — | UNTRACKED |\n   210→| Dramatic pause sound (FR-8.2) | later spec | dedicated audio spec | — | UNTRACKED |\n   211→| Victory sound (FR-8.3) | later spec | dedicated audio spec | — | UNTRACKED |\n   212→| Coin clink sound (FR-8.4) | later spec | dedicated audio spec | — | UNTRACKED |\n   213→\n   214→5 deferred items remain. All FR-5 and FR-7.6 items previously deferred are now **RESOLVED**.\n   215→\n   216→## Recommendations\n   217→\n   218→1. **Audio spec**: All 4 FR-8 items should be bundled into a dedicated audio/SFX spec covering sound design across all games. Low priority for launch.\n   219→\n   220→2. **Estimated wait time (FR-6.5)**: Self-deferred and low priority. Requires match fill-rate analytics data that doesn't exist yet. Safe to keep deferred past launch.\n   221→\n   222→3. **Frontend test coverage**: Zero vitest/component tests and zero Playwright E2E tests exist. Not an FR criterion but notable for launch readiness. Consider adding to E2E integration spec (203).\n   223→"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"c8e2c010-62bf-4268-abe7-c7c2643456f8","uuid":"46a546ad-a488-4485-a5a0-3f59cacc46d7","tool_use_result":{"type":"text","file":{"filePath":"/workspaces/rng-utopia/docs/specs/001-coinflip/gap-analysis.md","content":"# Gap Analysis: 001-coinflip — Coinflip\n\n- **Date**: 2026-02-26\n- **Spec status**: Done\n- **Previous analysis**: 2026-02-18 (pre-004 rewrite)\n\n## Implementation Inventory\n\n### On-Chain Instructions\n\n| Instruction | Program | File | Line |\n|------------|---------|------|------|\n| initialize_config | coinflip | programs/coinflip/src/instructions/initialize_config.rs | 24 |\n| create_match | coinflip | programs/coinflip/src/instructions/create_match.rs | 28 |\n| join_match | coinflip | programs/coinflip/src/instructions/join_match.rs | 25 |\n| claim_payout | coinflip | programs/coinflip/src/instructions/claim_payout.rs | 55 |\n| cancel_match | coinflip | programs/coinflip/src/instructions/cancel_match.rs | 24 |\n| timeout_cancel | coinflip | programs/coinflip/src/instructions/timeout_cancel.rs | 32 |\n| force_close | coinflip | programs/coinflip/src/instructions/force_close.rs | — |\n| initialize_platform | platform | programs/platform/src/instructions/initialize_platform.rs | 25 |\n| create_player_profile | platform | programs/platform/src/instructions/create_player_profile.rs | 24 |\n| update_player_profile | platform | programs/platform/src/instructions/update_player_profile.rs | 20 |\n\n**Architecture**: 3-tx flow — create → join(+Orao VRF request) → claim(+VRF read + settle). The previous `resolve_match` instruction was deleted in the 004 shared-infrastructure rewrite; resolution is now handled at claim time by reading Orao VRF randomness on-chain.\n\n### Shared Crate\n\n| Export | Module | File | Line |\n|--------|--------|------|------|\n| SIDE_HEADS / SIDE_TAILS | constants | shared/src/constants.rs | 2-3 |\n| PHASE_WAITING / LOCKED / SETTLED / CANCELLED | constants | shared/src/constants.rs | 6-9 |\n| LOCK_TIMEOUT_SECONDS (120) | constants | shared/src/constants.rs | 12 |\n| from_randomness | constants | shared/src/constants.rs | 15 |\n| TOTAL_FEE_BPS (300) | fees | shared/src/fees.rs | 5 |\n| calculate_fee | fees | shared/src/fees.rs | 12 |\n| split_fee | fees | shared/src/fees.rs | 17 |\n| TIER_AMOUNTS [6 tiers] | tiers | shared/src/tiers.rs | 5 |\n| get_tier_amount | tiers | shared/src/tiers.rs | 17 |\n| lifecycle::transition | lifecycle | shared/src/lifecycle.rs | — |\n| escrow (transfer helpers) | escrow | shared/src/escrow.rs | — |\n| timeout::is_expired | timeout | shared/src/timeout.rs | 12 |\n| pause::check_not_paused | pause | shared/src/pause.rs | 13 |\n| vrf_orao (read_orao_randomness, is_fulfilled) | vrf_orao | shared/src/vrf_orao.rs | 20 |\n| commit_reveal | commit_reveal | shared/src/commit_reveal.rs | — |\n| cpi (update_player_profile CPI) | cpi | shared/src/cpi.rs | — |\n\n### Game Engine Exports\n\n| Export | Package | File | Line |\n|--------|---------|------|------|\n| COINFLIP_PROGRAM_ID | game-engine | packages/game-engine/src/coinflip.ts | 10 |\n| getMatchPda | game-engine | packages/game-engine/src/coinflip.ts | 25 |\n| getConfigPda | game-engine | packages/game-engine/src/coinflip.ts | 36 |\n| getEntryAmount | game-engine | packages/game-engine/src/coinflip.ts | 48 |\n| calculatePotentialPayout | game-engine | packages/game-engine/src/coinflip.ts | 55 |\n| getOppositeSide | game-engine | packages/game-engine/src/coinflip.ts | 65 |\n| determineWinnerFromRandomness | game-engine | packages/game-engine/src/coinflip.ts | 72 |\n| CoinflipIDL / PlatformIDL | anchor-client | packages/anchor-client/src/index.ts | 10 |\n| Coinflip / Platform types | anchor-client | packages/anchor-client/src/index.ts | 6-7 |\n\n### Frontend Components\n\n| Component | File | Line |\n|-----------|------|------|\n| CoinflipProvider / useCoinflip | features/coinflip/context/CoinflipContext.tsx | 69, 362 |\n| CoinSideSelector | features/coinflip/components/CoinSideSelector.tsx | 19 |\n| CoinAnimation | features/coinflip/components/CoinAnimation.tsx | 20 |\n| OpenMatchesList | features/coinflip/components/OpenMatchesList.tsx | 31 |\n| MatchCard | features/coinflip/components/MatchCard.tsx | 13 |\n| ActiveMatchView | features/coinflip/components/ActiveMatchView.tsx | 12 |\n| chain.ts (instruction builders + queries + claimable matches) | features/coinflip/utils/chain.ts | 187-310 |\n| verification.ts (verifyMatch + VerificationResult) | features/coinflip/utils/verification.ts | — |\n| helpers.ts (truncateAddress, getOppositeSide) | features/coinflip/utils/helpers.ts | 3, 7 |\n| CoinflipPage | pages/CoinflipPage.tsx | 450 |\n| FairnessPage (coinflip VRF verification section) | App.tsx | — |\n\n### Tests\n\n| Test | Type | File | Status |\n|------|------|------|--------|\n| initialize_config (1 test) | bankrun | solana/tests/coinflip.ts:360 | passing |\n| create_match (4 tests) | bankrun | solana/tests/coinflip.ts:379-435 | passing |\n| join_match (3 tests) | bankrun | solana/tests/coinflip.ts:461-513 | passing |\n| claim_payout (9 tests, incl. CPI) | bankrun | solana/tests/coinflip.ts:554-757 | passing |\n| cancel_match (3 tests) | bankrun | solana/tests/coinflip.ts:793-827 | passing |\n| timeout_cancel (3 tests) | bankrun | solana/tests/coinflip.ts:855-909 | passing |\n| full lifecycle (3 tests) | bankrun | solana/tests/coinflip.ts:934-985 | passing |\n| platform program (5 tests) | bankrun | solana/tests/platform.ts:97-203 | passing |\n| Frontend unit/component tests | vitest | — | none exist |\n| E2E tests | playwright | — | none exist |\n\n**Total: 31 bankrun tests passing (26 coinflip + 5 platform), 0 frontend tests, 0 E2E tests.**\n\n## Acceptance Criteria Audit\n\n### FR-1: Match Creation\n\n| # | Criterion | Status | Evidence |\n|---|-----------|--------|----------|\n| 1 | Player can select one of six tiers (Iron–Diamond) | SATISFIED | shared/src/tiers.rs:5 TIER_AMOUNTS, types.ts:25 TIER_AMO