{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_0167SZpHWYz888exQD88pRBj","type":"tool_result","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Perfect! Now I have all the information needed to create a comprehensive inventory. Let me compile the final report:\n\n## Solana Coinflip Program Inventory\n\n### 1. INSTRUCTION HANDLERS - Coinflip Program\n\n**Location**: `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/solana/programs/coinflip/src/instructions/`\n\n| Handler | File | Key Logic |\n|---------|------|-----------|\n| `initialize_config` | `initialize_config.rs:24-32` | Creates singleton config PDA with authority and treasury; sets paused=false |\n| `create_match` | `create_match.rs:37-72` | Creates match in Waiting phase; validates tier & side; transfers entry amount to match PDA escrow; stores creator pubkey, tier, side, timestamps |\n| `join_match` | `join_match.rs:54-99` | Validates Waiting→Locked transition; checks opponent ≠ creator; transfers opponent's entry amount; requests Orao VRF with match PDA as seed; updates match with opponent, phase=Locked, resolve_deadline, vrf_request_key |\n| `claim_payout` | `claim_payout.rs:68-179` | Validates Locked phase & !claimed; reads Orao randomness; derives winner from randomness[0]%2; calculates fee & payout; transfers to winner & treasury; updates both player profiles via CPI; emits MatchSettled event; closes match PDA (rent to creator) |\n| `cancel_match` | `cancel_match.rs:25-39` | Only allows from Waiting phase (before opponent joins); closes match PDA returning all lamports to creator |\n| `timeout_cancel` | `timeout_cancel.rs:40-88` | Validates Locked phase & deadline expired; checks VRF NOT fulfilled; refunds both players' entry amounts; transitions to Refunded; closes PDA (rent to creator) |\n| `force_close` | `force_close.rs:30-45` | Admin-only (validates authority from config); drains all lamports from match account to recipient; zeroes account data (for migration/recovery) |\n\n---\n\n### 2. STATE 