ty: Pubkey` — Admin authority\n  - `treasury: Pubkey` — Treasury wallet for fees\n  - `fee_bps: u16` — Total fee in basis points (300)\n  - `bump: u8` — PDA bump seed\n\n#### `PlayerProfile` (lines 18-35)\n- **PDA Seed**: `[b\"player_profile\", wallet.as_ref()]`\n- **Fields**:\n  - `authority: Pubkey` — Player's wallet\n  - `total_games: u64` — Games played\n  - `wins: u64` — Games won\n  - `total_wagered: u64` — Total SOL wagered (lamports)\n  - `total_won: u64` — Total SOL won (lamports)\n  - `bump: u8` — PDA bump seed\n\n---\n\n### 8. ERROR CODES - Platform Program\n\n**Location**: `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/solana/programs/platform/src/error.rs`\n\n| Error Code | Anchor Code | Message |\n|-----------|-----------|---------|\n| `Unauthorized` | 6100 | Unauthorized: signer is not the admin authority |\n\n---\n\n### 9. BANKRUN TESTS\n\n#### Coinflip Tests\n**File**: `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/solana/tests/coinflip.ts`\n**Total**: 26 tests\n\n| Test Name | Line | Category |\n|-----------|------|----------|\n| `creates config with treasury and paused=false` | 360 | initialize_config |\n| `creates match in Waiting phase with correct escrow` | 379 | create_match |\n| `escrows correct lamport amount` | 395 | create_match |\n| `rejects invalid side` | 414 | create_match |\n| `rejects invalid tier` | 435 | create_match |\n| `transitions to Locked, doubles escrow, sets VRF fields` | 461 | join_match |\n| `rejects self-join` | 486 | join_match |\n| `rejects join when already Locked` | 513 | join_match |\n| `creator wins with HEADS, fee to treasury` | 554 | claim_payout |\n| `opponent wins with TAILS` | 582 | claim_payout |\n| `either player can trigger claim — payout goes to derived winner` | 610 | claim_payout |\n| `match PDA closed after claim` | 634 | claim_payout |\n| `rejects claim with unfulfilled randomness` | 648 | claim_payout |\n| `rejects double claim (account closed)` | 666 | claim_payout |\n| `rejects unauthorized caller (not crea