-------|------|----------|\n| `creates config with treasury and paused=false` | 360 | initialize_config |\n| `creates match in Waiting phase with correct escrow` | 379 | create_match |\n| `escrows correct lamport amount` | 395 | create_match |\n| `rejects invalid side` | 414 | create_match |\n| `rejects invalid tier` | 435 | create_match |\n| `transitions to Locked, doubles escrow, sets VRF fields` | 461 | join_match |\n| `rejects self-join` | 486 | join_match |\n| `rejects join when already Locked` | 513 | join_match |\n| `creator wins with HEADS, fee to treasury` | 554 | claim_payout |\n| `opponent wins with TAILS` | 582 | claim_payout |\n| `either player can trigger claim — payout goes to derived winner` | 610 | claim_payout |\n| `match PDA closed after claim` | 634 | claim_payout |\n| `rejects claim with unfulfilled randomness` | 648 | claim_payout |\n| `rejects double claim (account closed)` | 666 | claim_payout |\n| `rejects unauthorized caller (not creator or opponent)` | 685 | claim_payout |\n| `updates player profiles via CPI — creator wins` | 726 | claim_payout |\n| `updates player profiles via CPI — opponent wins` | 757 | claim_payout |\n| `creator cancels Waiting match, full refund` | 793 | cancel_match |\n| `rejects cancel after Locked (CannotCancel)` | 811 | cancel_match |\n| `rejects cancel by non-creator` | 827 | cancel_match |\n| `permissionless refund after deadline when VRF unfulfilled` | 855 | timeout_cancel |\n| `rejects timeout before deadline` | 892 | timeout_cancel |\n| `rejects timeout when VRF IS fulfilled — must claim instead` | 909 | timeout_cancel |\n| `create → join → claim(HEADS) → PDA closed` | 934 | full lifecycle |\n| `create → cancel → create again` | 966 | full lifecycle |\n| `create → join → timeout (VRF unfulfilled) → both refunded` | 985 | full lifecycle |\n\n#### Platform Tests\n**File**: `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/solana/tests/platform.ts`\n**Total**: 5 tests\n\n| Test Name | Line | Category |\n|-----------|------|----------|\n| `creates config with authority, treasury, and fee_bps` | 97 | initialize_platform |\n| `rejects double initialization` | 111 | initialize_platform |\n| `creates a player profile with zeroed stats` | 129 | create_player_profile |\n| `different wallets get different profiles` | 152 | create_player_profile |\n| `rejects double profile creation` | 203 | create_player_profile |\n\n---\n\n### Summary Statistics\n\n- **Coinflip Instructions**: 7 handlers\n- **Platform Instructions**: 3 handlers\n- **Coinflip State Accounts**: 2 types + 1 event\n- **Platform State Accounts**: 2 types\n- **Shared Crate Modules**: 11 modules with cross-cutting utilities\n- **Total Bankrun Tests**: 31 (26 coinflip + 5 platform)\n- **Error Codes**: 12 coinflip + 1 platform = 13 total\n- **Tier System**: 6 tiers (Iron, Bronze, Silver, Gold, Platinum, Diamond) with fixed lamport amounts"}],"totalDurationMs":74946,"totalTokens":77515,"totalToolUseCount":40,"usage":{"input_tokens":4,"cache_creation_input_tokens":1247,"cache_read_input_tokens":72271,"output_tokens":3993,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":1247,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[],"speed":"standard"}}}
